{"id":81278,"title":"Motivating patients.","abstract":"Patients who seek advice and treatment for periodontal conditions often find challenges in the personal involvement required for successful care. This paper reviews methods of advising and motivating patients to adhere to oral hygiene regimens and understand the necessity for long-term management of the condition. ","date":"2014-09-09","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25198635","annotations":[{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.404711,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Hygiene","weight":0.278001,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hygiene"},{"name":"Mouth","weight":0.268282,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouth"},{"name":"Oral hygiene","weight":0.137801,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oral_hygiene"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Paper","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paper"},{"name":"Periodontology","weight":0.0166129,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Periodontology"},{"name":"Causality","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Causality"}]}
